      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="number">2</div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="item-title">Desafío</div>
          <div class="item-subtitle">Competitividad</div>
          <div class="item-description">
            <p>
              ¿Cómo mantener la calidad del servicio mientras reduces costos en un entorno cada vez
              más competitivo?
            </p>
            <div class="grid">
              <div class="grid-item">
                <h4>Experiencia de cliente</h4>
                <p>
                  Los clientes esperan respuestas inmediatas y personalizadas, 24/7, sin importar el
                  canal de comunicación.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="grid-item">
                <h4>Recursos limitados</h4>
                <p>
                  Contratar más personal incrementa los costos operativos significativamente y no es
                  una solución escalable.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="effects">
          <div class="effect">Efecto Scroll</div>
          <div class="effect">Blur</div>
          <div class="effect">Hover</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline-item">
        <div class="number">3</div>
        <div class="content">
          <div class="item-title">Solución</div>
          <div class="item-subtitle">Futuro hoy</div>
          <div class="item-description">
            <p>Implementa Agentes IA RAG y reduce 70% de estos costos, con autonomía 24/7.</p>
            <div class="grid">
              <div class="grid-item">
                <h4>Atención continua</h4>
                <p>
                  Servicio sin interrupciones todo el año, mejorando la experiencia de tus clientes
                  y aumentando la satisfacción.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="grid-item">
                <h4>Eficiencia operativa</h4>
                <p>
                  Reducción drástica en tiempos de respuesta y costos operativos, permitiéndote
                  enfocar recursos en áreas estratégicas.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="button">Descubre cómo implementarlo →</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="effects">
          <div class="effect">Efecto Scroll</div>
          <div class="effect">Blur</div>
          <div class="effect">Hover</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="diagram-annotations">
    <div class="annotation" style="top: 50px; left: 20px;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Título principal - Se mantiene fijo</div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation" style="top: 90px; left: 20px;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Subtítulo con elemento "low-cost" resaltado</div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation" style="top: 180px; left: 10px;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Números grandes con efecto visual</div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation" style="top: 250px; right: 30px;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Efecto blur en boxes</div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation" style="top: 340px; right: 60px;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Activación por scroll (GSAP)</div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation" style="top: 430px; right: 50px;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Efecto hover en elementos interactivos</div>
    </div>

    <div class="annotation" style="top: 520px; left: 50%;">
      <div class="annotation-dot"></div>
      <div class="annotation-line"></div>
      <div class="annotation-text">Diseño grid responsive para bloques</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="legend">
    <h3>Leyenda</h3>
    <div class="legend-item">
      <span class="legend-color scroll-color"></span>
      <span>Efecto de activación por scroll (GSAP)</span>
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item">
      <span class="legend-color blur-color"></span>
      <span>Efecto backdrop-blur</span>
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item">
      <span class="legend-color hover-color"></span>
      <span>Animaciones al pasar el cursor</span>
    </div>
    <div class="legend-item">
      <span class="legend-color number-color"></span>
      <span>Números grandes (1, 2, 3)</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="responsive-notes">
    <h3>Notas de responsividad</h3>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="device-name">Desktop</div>
      <div class="device-desc">
        Diseño en columnas con el número a la izquierda (20%) y contenido a la derecha (80%)
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="device-name">Tablet</div>
      <div class="device-desc">
        Reducción del tamaño de la fuente y distribución adaptable del grid
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="device">
      <div class="device-name">Mobile</div>
      <div class="device-desc">
        Número en la parte superior y contenido debajo, con grid en formato de una columna
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .diagram-container {
    font-family:
      system-ui,
      -apple-system,
      BlinkMacSystemFont,
      'Segoe UI',
      Roboto,
      sans-serif;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    background-color: #1a1a1a;
    color: #f5f5f5;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .section-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .section-title h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff7e00, #ffbe0b);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .section-title p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #aaa;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .timeline-structure {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background-color: #242424;
    padding: 30px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .header {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .title-section {
    border-left: 5px solid #ff9e00;
    padding-left: 15px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #ffb700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .subtitle::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    background-color: #ffb700;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .timeline-items {
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-items::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 100px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, #ff9e00 15%, #ff9e00 85%, transparent);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .number {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    margin-right: 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e00, #ff7600);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.5);
    z-index: 2;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .content {
    flex: 1;
    background-color: #2a2a2a;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    position: relative;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .content::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -10px;
    top: 30px;
    width: 10px;
    height: 20px;
    background-color: #2a2a2a;
    clip-path: polygon(100% 0, 0 50%, 100% 100%);
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .item-title {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #ff9e00;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .item-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #eee;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .item-description {
    color: #ccc;
  }

  .item-description p {
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .item-box {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .item-box ul {
    list-style-type: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .item-box li {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    padding-left: 25px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .item-box li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 8px;
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background-color: #ff9e00;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .item-box li span {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-top: 15px;
  }

  .grid-item {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 15px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .grid-item h4 {
    color: #ff9e00;
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .grid-item h4::before {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    margin-right: 8px;
    background-color: #ff9e00;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .button {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e00, #ff7600);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-top: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.3);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .effects {
    position: absolute;
    right: -60px;
    top: 20px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .effect {
    background-color: #333;
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #fff;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 100px;
  }

  .effect:nth-child(1) {
    background-color: #4c83ff;
  }

  .effect:nth-child(2) {
    background-color: #9333ea;
  }

  .effect:nth-child(3) {
    background-color: #10b981;
  }

  .diagram-annotations {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .annotation {
    position: absolute;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .annotation-dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    background-color: #ff9e00;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid #fff;
  }

  .annotation-line {
    width: 40px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.7);
    margin: 0 5px;
  }

  .annotation-text {
    background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #fff;
    backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 158, 0, 0.3);
    max-width: 200px;
  }

  .legend {
    margin-top: 40px;
    background-color: #242424;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .legend h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .legend-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .legend-color {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-radius: 4px;
    margin-right: 10px;
  }

  .scroll-color {
    background-color: #4c83ff;
  }

  .blur-color {
    background-color: #9333ea;
  }

  .hover-color {
    background-color: #10b981;
  }

  .number-color {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9e00, #ff7600);
  }

  .responsive-notes {
    margin-top: 40px;
    background-color: #242424;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .responsive-notes h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .device {
    display: flex;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
  }

  .device:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }

  .device-name {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #ff9e00;
    width: 100px;
  }

  .device-desc {
    flex: 1;
    color: #ccc;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .timeline-items::before {
      left: 30px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .number {
      width: 60px;
      height: 60px;
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-right: 0;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .content::before {
      display: none;
    }

    .grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .effects {
      position: relative;
      right: auto;
      top: auto;
      flex-direction: row;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .effect {
      flex: 1;
    }

    .diagram-annotations {
      display: none;
    }
  }
</style>
